vulnerabilities.title: js-object-utilities Vulnerable to Prototype Pollution
vulnerabilities.description:
**Vulnerability type:**
Prototype Pollution

**Affected Package:**
* Product: js-object-utilities
* Version: 2.2.0

**Remedy:**

Update package to version 2.2.1.

**Vulnerability Location(s):**
```js
at module.exports (/node_modules/js-object-utilities/dist/set.js:16:29)
```
